name: Ella Moss
description:
Chic pair of lightweight, textured, slim leg pants from Ella Moss in black with the style name Serena featuring a pleated waistband and side zip closure.
 These pants are a women's size XS and measures 15 across the waist laid flat with an inseam of 28 and a rise of 10. 
 These pants are made of a polyester and spandex blend crepe and are new and unused with the tag still attached.
 Original retail $178.
